<br>
2 Level 65 warriors, Both at 41% haste.  One with Norge`Tal, the other with BBB.   Both warriors would attack at same time and neither would taunt.   Norge`Tal showed to be a consistent winner in the aggro department over about 30 mins.  The warrior with the BBB then switched to BoC/Cord Hilted meat tenderizer from Xanamech, and we did the same thing.    BBB/Hammer was the clear winner between the two.<br>
<br>
